```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "details": {
    "script_name": "pyfr-script",
    "nodes": 3,
    "exclusive": true,
    "gpu_bind": "closest",
    "use_min_nodes": true,
    "time": "0-06:00:00",
    "memory": "80G",
    "output_file": "pyfr-build-hip.out",
    "requeue": false,
    "partition": "amd",
    "tasks": 9,
    "gpus": 3,
    "cpus_per_gpu": 8,
    "environment": {
      "rocm": "6.0.0",
      "gcc": "BUILD_GCC_VER",
      "python": "BUILD_PYTHON_VER",
      "libffi": "BUILD_LIBFFI_VER",
      "openssl": "BUILD_OPENSSL_VER",
      "mpich": "BUILD_MPICH_VER",
      "ucx": "BUILD_UCX_VER",
      "openmpi": "BUILD_OPENMPI_VER"
    },
    "software": {
      "pyfr": "BUILD_PATH/pyfr.build",
      "mpi4py": "python3 -c 'from mpi4py import MPI; print(MPI.COMM_WORLD.Get_rank())'",
      "mpirun": "mpirun -n ${np}"
    },
    "resources": {
      "cpu": "SLURM_NTASKS",
      "nodes": "SLURM_JOB_NUM_NODES",
      "mpi_tasks_per_node": "SLURM_TASKS_PER_NODE"
    }
  }
}
```
